message.body: Ok so Seybolt is coming Monday at 5pm.... It will be 92$ I figured it out n called Qtown, they would be atleast 105$ which isn't too much more but every penny counts plus I'd rather give my small vet the business...
So if ur not gonna be there Seybolt asked if u could leave some basic info on lucky... His name u want on coggins, where u want coggins sent n a check for 92$ (for rhino/flu, ptw, rabies & coggins).
He will come back out again later in spring to give next round that Tanya/Brenna wants
Ok, awesome! I'm doing stalls&pm feed on Monday so I'll be around. Thanks for arranging it!
Great! No problem:) I wish everyone would use him haha his call fee is 20$ n he splits it between however many horses he sees... So it will be 10$ for each of us. Qtown is $60 call fee!!
We would all pay like 2$ for call fee if everyone used him haha
Yeah I guess it's nice to have qtown for emergencies but they are pricey and recommend pricey stuff too! Nice to have options.
